    • getTTestPValue

      public double getTTestPValue(int att, ClusStatManager stat_manager)
      Computes a 2-sample t statistic, without the hypothesis of equal sub-population variances, and returns the p-value of a t test. t = (m1 - m2) / sqrt(var1/n1 + var2/n2);
      Parameters:
      att - attribute index
      Returns:
      t p-value
